snippet.title: Evil Mineswifter (Minesweeper) Gameplay
snippet.description:
Unsolvable Minesweeper – the perfect gift for someone else. Evil Mineswifter is a decidedly evil Minesweeper game for macOS and iOS.

Download on the App Store:
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/id1523249883

Learn more:
https://bonzaiapps.com/evil-mineswifter/
